COSCO Pac mulls buying port terminals . COSCO Pacific Ltd said on Wednesday it was considering buying port terminals from parent COSCO ( Hong Kong ) Group Ltd . " It will include six port terminals in China , such as in Qingdao , Shekou , Ningbo and Yingkou in Liaoning , and another three in Asia , " said Zhang Dachun , vice chairman of COSCO Pacific , in a press briefing . Zhang declined to comment on the size of investment involved but said " we have sufficient funds to invest in any projects if the opportunity arises . " Kelvin Wong , a director of COSCO Pacific said the company would expand its fleet and port terminals operation on expectation of a pick up in the shipping industry . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6370 
